{"tid":1854114,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"早幾日揸架fk7去拜年比人笑 大家幫我評評理","createTime":"2020-01-31T10:26:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-06T14:00:32.000Z","uid":153,"like":37,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"6aa79e16d736410256e2cf382aef7b76c1aa91ae","tid":1854114,"uid":153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T10:26:55.000Z","msg":"早兩日去親戚度食飯 走嗰陣時車埋姨仔佢一家人<br />\n<br />\n佢地上車之後：<br />\n佢個仔：媽媽呢隻車咪我地成日uber坐個隻？<br />\n姨仔：係喎個架咪唔知咩Toyota，幾好坐架！<br />\n我：我依架honda黎架，都係日本車！<br />\n佢老公：老婆，我地平時坐果架toyota咪prius囉<br />\n姨仔：哦！估唔到honda都有出架同prius差唔多既車，哈哈！<br />\n佢個仔：咁表哥係咪係做uber架？<br />\n<br />\n之後我已經開始黑面 全程hea鳩佢地算<br />\n<br />\n落車個時<br />\n姨仔：唔該晒呀姨甥仔！你架車仲好坐過toyota個隻！好穩呀！<br />\n<br />\n跟手已經88<br />\n<br />\n我屌你老母！似閪？<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.gotuning.com/images/products/42703-1885-45_10.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gotuning.com%2Fimages%2Fproducts%2F42703-1885-45_10.JPG&h=54fa3528&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gYGH5K2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgYGH5K2.jpg&h=0f348adb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ef93cb749ccc7305a0a9e92b4c2b0d121f59ee4b","tid":1854114,"uid":198536,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T10:29:21.000Z","msg":"第一張圖部prius改到咁柒既<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7c1379e8ef6302cf496913d8b7f4bb7e29b53a0","tid":1854114,"uid":771,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T10:29:30.000Z","msg":"笑死，好撚似"},{"pid":"f30f9a037413e6e2eab619c61f8a890724b394df","tid":1854114,"uid":163347,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T10:33:44.000Z","msg":"嗰d 人唔撚識車由得佢啦...<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nSorry 我笑咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a119a8584e96472c11813e38faf6fcf219deafa6","tid":1854114,"uid":316537,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T10:38:47.0